'''''{{lang|la|Lepidochitona}}'''''是[[多板纲|多板纲]][[新石鳖亞綱|新石鳖亞綱]][[石鳖目|石鳖目]][[鬃毛石鱉總科|鬃毛石鱉總科]][[Lepidochitonidae|Lepidochitonidae]]科之下的一個[[屬_(生物)|屬]]。本屬曾被編入[[Tonicellidae|Tonicellidae]]、[[薄石鱉科|薄石鱉科]]<ref>{{cite journal |authors=Petraccioli, A., et al. |year=2012 |url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3834572/ |title=Chromosomes of ''Lepidochitona caprearum'' (Scacchi, 1836) (Polyplacophora, Acanthochitonina, Tonicellidae) provide insights into Acanthochitonina karyological evolution.|journal=''Comparative Cytogenetics'' |volume=6 |issue=4 |pages=397-407 |language=en }}</ref>。

''[[Lepidochitona_raymondi|L. raymondi]]''是多板綱唯一的一個[[雌雄間性|雌雄間性]]物種<ref>{{cite book  | url = http://books.google.ca/books?id=CKautf2EUPkC  | title = Monograph of living chitons (Mollusca: Polyplacophora)  | isbn = 9789004074149  | author1 = Kaas, P  | author2 = Van Belle, R. A  | year = 1985  | access-date = 2015-06-05  | archive-date = 2014-11-29  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129040726/http://books.google.ca/books?id=CKautf2EUPkC  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。

本屬包括有不少[[化石種|化石種]]，但今時今日亦有[[現生種|現生種]]<ref>{{cite journal |authors=Dell'Angelo, B., et al. |year=2011 |url=http://www.chitons.it/pdf/DellAngelo_2011_W_WA_fossils%20rb.pdf |title=Chitons (Polyplacophora) from Paleogene strata in western Washington State, USA. |journal=[[Journal_of_Paleontology|Journal of Paleontology]] |volume=85 |issue=5 |pages=936-954 |language=en |access-date=2015-06-05 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221956/http://www.chitons.it/pdf/DellAngelo_2011_W_WA_fossils%20rb.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

